      "text": "Sigrid Eskilsdotter (Banér)\nSigrid Eskilsdotter (Banér) (died 1527), was a Swedish noble, the mother of the Swedish regent Christina Gyllenstierna and the maternal grandmother of King Gustav Vasa of Sweden.",
      "score_breakdown": {
