      "title": "Loekman Hakim",
      "score": 0.06437803142133608,
      "text": "Loekman Hakim\nLoekman Hakim was born in Cianjur, West Java, Indonesia, on December 30, 1975, to Eman Sulaeman and Iis Martini. Loekman is the third child of five siblings. His father was a teacher at SMP 5 Bandung. Loekman married Rika Nurhayati and have two child.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.0765939348182151,
